practically nothing.

37:25.418 --> 37:26.620
So it's
all about money?

37:31.992 --> 37:36.093
Ah Sarah, for God's
sake, have a bit of sense.

37:36.095 --> 37:38.298
What do you take me
for in God's name?

37:39.231 --> 37:40.367
I should've known.

37:41.800 --> 37:43.367
In all the years of being
your fool of a mistress,

37:43.369 --> 37:46.370
you've been messing around
with your wife behind my back.

37:46.372 --> 37:48.305
Ah for heaven's sake.

37:48.307 --> 37:49.573
Don't be so ridiculous.

37:49.575 --> 37:50.774
I would never think

37:50.776 --> 37:52.646
of any other woman
like that besides you.

37:53.512 --> 37:54.913
Especially my wife.

37:57.182 --> 37:58.983
What's going on, over.

38:34.354 --> 38:37.055
How could you
have not known about this?

38:37.057 --> 38:38.189
Me?

38:38.191 --> 38:40.490
Ye were the ones
putting it in the bags.

38:40.492 --> 38:41.959
Yeah, but you're the one

38:41.961 --> 38:43.428
who's been monitoring the
safe for the last two months.

38:43.430 --> 38:46.129
