Too many bubbles.

38:59.778 --> 39:01.044
And they're
just not good anymore?

39:01.046 --> 39:01.947
No, they're not.

39:03.148 --> 39:04.881
Well I mean at least
we have some in euro.

39:04.883 --> 39:08.019
I mean it's probably
like 20,000.

39:08.021 --> 39:09.486
Hm, that's not too bad.

39:09.488 --> 39:14.191
But there must be three times
that amount in Irish pounds.

39:14.193 --> 39:17.394
I just don't understand why he
didn't change them into euros

39:17.396 --> 39:18.629
when he had the chance.

39:18.631 --> 39:20.263
Well maybe changing
over a large sum of cash

39:20.265 --> 39:22.200
