would've been a red flag

39:22.202 --> 39:23.533
to the tax department.

39:23.535 --> 39:26.236
The central bank,
it's our only option.

39:26.238 --> 39:27.771
How
is that an option?

39:27.773 --> 39:32.075
They still exchange
Irish pounds, they have to.

39:32.077 --> 39:33.878
Look, even even if they do,

39:33.880 --> 39:35.613
we can't just wander
in there with wads

39:35.615 --> 39:37.414
of outdated cash in our hands.

39:37.416 --> 39:38.615
Why not?

39:38.617 --> 39:40.117
Well because what
are we supposed to say?

39:40.119 --> 39:41.619
Oh oh you know this morning
I was changing the sheets

39:41.621 --> 39:43.687
