quid just happened

39:43.689 --> 39:46.023
to fall out from
under my mattress.

39:46.025 --> 39:48.725
We can do it in stages.

39:48.727 --> 39:50.363
Use the hairdryer.

39:52.097 --> 39:54.631
Sure, people are always
finding stacks of money

39:54.633 --> 39:58.236
