money in for the last,

40:15.488 --> 40:18.155
you know three or four decades.

40:18.157 --> 40:20.490
Yeah, nothing
suspicious about that.

40:20.492 --> 40:22.093
Yeah, and isn't the
central bank in Dublin?

40:22.095 --> 40:23.561
Yeah, it is.

